[tool]
[tool.poetry]
name = "MetaNaviT"
version = "0.1.0"
description = ""
authors = [ "Kaitlyn Laurie <k.laurie124@gmail.com>" ]
readme = "README.md"

[tool.poetry.scripts]
generate = "app.engine.generate:generate_datasource"
dev = "run:dev"
setup = "setup:main"
build = "run:build"

[tool.poetry.dependencies]
python = ">=3.11,<3.12"
fastapi = "^0.109.1"
python-dotenv = "^1.0.0"
pydantic = ">=2.0.0"
aiostream = "^0.5.2"
cachetools = "^5.3.3"
llama-index = "^0.12.11"
rich = "^13.9.4"
llama-index-llms-ollama = "^0.5.0"
llama-index-embeddings-nomic = "^0.6.0"
llama-index-vector-stores-postgres = "^0.4.1"
pgvector = "^0.3.6"
psycopg2-binary = "^2.9.10"
flake8 = "^7.1.1"
llama-index-readers-file = "^0.4.4"
transformers = "^4.48.3"
torch = "2.2.1"
nomic = "^3.4.1"
llama-index-embeddings-huggingface = "0.4.0"
llama-index-embeddings-instructor = "^0.3.0"


[tool.poetry.dependencies.uvicorn]
extras = [ "standard" ]
version = "^0.23.2"

[tool.poetry.dependencies.docx2txt]
version = "^0.8"

[tool.poetry.group]
[tool.poetry.group.dev]
[tool.poetry.group.dev.dependencies]
mypy = "^1.8.0"
pytest = "^8.3.4"
pytest-asyncio = "^0.25.3"
pytest-mock = "^3.14.0"
httpx = "^0.28.1"
pytest-cov = "^6.0.0"
deepeval = "^2.3.0"

[tool.mypy]
python_version = "3.11"
plugins = "pydantic.mypy"
exclude = [ "tests", "venv", ".venv", "output", "config" ]
check_untyped_defs = true
warn_unused_ignores = false
show_error_codes = true
namespace_packages = true
ignore_missing_imports = true
follow_imports = "silent"
implicit_optional = true
strict_optional = false
disable_error_code = [ "return-value", "assignment" ]

[[tool.mypy.overrides]]
module = "app.*"
ignore_missing_imports = false

[build-system]
requires = [ "poetry-core" ]
build-backend = "poetry.core.masonry.api"

[tool.pytest.ini_options]
asyncio_mode = "strict"
asyncio_default_fixture_loop_scope = "function"
testpaths = ["tests"]
pythonpath = [
    ".",
    "app"
]
addopts = "-v -s"

config.loaders.yaml:
file_system:
  # Base directory to start crawling from
  path: "datasets/file_organization/Easy/"
  # Optional crawler settings
  max_workers: 4
  batch_size: 1000
  # Optional file exclusion patterns
  exclude:
    - "**/*.git/*"
    - "**/*.pyc"
    - "**/node_modules/*"
    - "**/__pycache__/*"

  # connection: connection string
  # queries: list of queries to run
